  "summary" : "The proposed Unified Layer by NPCI aims to provide a centralized, interoperable platform for government agencies and banks to manage Direct Benefit Transfer (DBT) and welfare schemes using Central Bank Digital Currency (CBDC). It will standardize data exchange for beneficiary details, scheme parameters, and fund unlocking requests, replacing the current one-to-one integration model. This layer will facilitate secure, controlled, and auditable information flow, reducing operational complexity and implementation effort.",
